==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
# A language spoken in [[Mali]] by as many six million people.  Fewer numbers of people speak or understand the language, or dialects of it, in [[Burkina Faso]], [[Côte d'Ivoire]], and [[Gambia]].

